。辯方及後呈上Twitter片段及相片，顯示有警員出入博物館，A稱不清楚進入博物館的警員是否包括他本人，惟確認離開博物館的是他及同袍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210323/6GWEZO5E2JHLZBQVCSUA57L47Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210323%2F6GWEZO5E2JHLZBQVCSUA57L47Y%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=58bcc924\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210323%2F6GWEZO5E2JHLZBQVCSUA57L47Y%2F&h=6edabab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210323/6GWEZO5E2JHLZBQVCSUA57L47Y/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"飛虎都咁智障? 你明唔明狗點解 有乜關係? 要你同意?<br />\n依家講緊要證明市民明白咩叫&quot;有狗入左去&quot;<br />\n就證明到影張相其實冇用 大家一早知wo"},{"pid":"3be0b3b6e0918c11393490c200fdef74e775b3c5","tid":2457591,"uid":384207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"吳太盛既同袍智商都有返咁上下"},{"pid":"7d848ab6bb43d9ec5ca1a069963d0946917b529a","tid":2457591,"uid":319935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cb9342d0f0a887e60a45fa6401390cb53533ac","tid":2457591,"uid":66,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b4a7b0cad8c48f3b834b874f89a9634be5af95","tid":2457591,"uid":30836,"like":931,"dislike":2,"score":929,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"辯方聞言問A，知否示威者一般以「狗」形容警察，A則謂：「汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"Outout outoutout"},{"pid":"138f8e5c71cdc3fbc9f9afa0a72e02ff0602f139","tid":2457591,"uid":93717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T02:41:18.000Z","msg":"狗都不如呀"},{"pid":"93a470e54222f9229218ebc391fa94f223aee547","tid":2457591,"uid"